      • injectionStrategy

        protected InjectionStrategy injectionStrategy
        Position to inject the mod file at in the class path, if blank injects at the bottom as usual, alternatively the developer can specify "top" to inject at the top, "base" to inject above the game jar, or "above: name" to inject above a specified other library matching "name".
